EN: The large farm has a total area of eight hundred hectares.

ZH: 这片土地可以划分成几公顷的小块。
EN: This piece of land can be divided into several hectares.

ZH: 这片沙漠跨越了数百公顷。
EN: This desert spans hundreds of hectares.

